{"type": "article", "id": 4373, "title": "索尼 Qrio 智能门锁", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-15T07:55:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233038psbOyJuavhm2dnQt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本电子产品品牌索尼最近新作不断，继早前发布了 E-Paper 纸质电子手表之后，日前又带来了一款名为「Qrio」的智能门锁，配置有手机解锁、与家人朋友分享解锁密匙等基础功能。而与如今市面上大多数智能门锁不同的是，Qrio 并不需要你更换掉原有的门锁，而只需将这款智能门锁安装在原来的普通版门锁上即可使用。目前，Qrio 正在日本众筹网站 Makuake 上众筹，起售价 15000 日元（约合人民币 780 元），<a href=\"https://www.makuake.com/project/qrio-smart-lock/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233036VM6nJ7bdNlu2PfBK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233036rbkise8KGphz3JmD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233037ibKOrZLloRcNateT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233037se7ANGndjI0bh3Qm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}